{"tid":1307643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主線！！！！五大訴求，勿忘初衷呀！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:50:19.000Z","uid":60661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ddf291936749be5be1ac855aca52d16e001ff9","tid":1307643,"uid":60661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"今日已經係7月12號啦，距離612已經一個月啦！<br />\n今日去完梁烈士既公祭，我真係覺得好對唔住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n件事發生左一個月，我地仲係咩都爭取唔到<br />\n大家好似已經唔記得左我地既五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民陣已經宣佈左721將會係金鐘舉行集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/orV06En.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2ForV06En.jpg&h=9afaf486&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大家今次一定要集中\b火力同精神準備今次集會<br />\n上次7月7啲狗咬人咬得咁惡 我地一定要比返啲顏色佢地睇<br />\n巴打們！GEAR UPPPP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次冇藉口再比遊行人數跌落去啦，上次已經得返二十幾萬<br />\n今次起碼要推返上破百萬，話比林鄭知我地既立場企得好硬，不撤不退！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求︰<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span></span></strong><br />\n我地唔可以比死去既人既生命白白浪費！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/11/235651_0cff9910eba93618e39618e3941b5afc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F11%2F235651_0cff9910eba93618e39618e3941b5afc.png&h=24f46b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連儂場寶礦力嗰啲唔係唔搞 但眼前呢個集會係最重要 大家要叫返身邊既人出黎<br />\n大家可以比返佢地睇 612 77 啲狗點亂咬人 激發返佢地既鬥志<br />\n只要今次贏左 連儂牆慢慢起都得 寶礦力飲到嘔都得呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766d94a8ad378d7607d9c16698173ca17493993a","tid":1307643,"uid":60661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}